name: You are endless blooming
description:
"Regardless of the damage or the so -called filth, even the broken wooden walls of your yard
But always focused on your colorful and lush bloom, believing in your infinite potential, always exist."

("Hindi alintana ang kasiraan o ang masasabing karumiran, maging ang baling  kahoy na dingding ng iyong bakuran
Kundi laging nakatuon sa makukulay at mayabong mong pamumulaklak, naaniniwala sa walang hanggan mong potensyal, laging umiiral.")
